{"title":"Park Tool derailleur hanger alignment tool gets a modern update with all new DAG-3","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/08/park-tool-derailleur-hanger-alignment-tool-gets-a-modern-update-with-all-new-dag-3/","date":1615236340000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>For decades, the Park Derailleur Alignment Gauge has been a fixture of bike shops all over the globe. Most recently, the DAG-2.2 was given some key updates to work with modern frames. But with arguably better tools from other tool builders out there, Park needed to head back to the drawing board to come up with something completely new. Something like the DAG-3.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08152812/Park-Tool-DAG-3-derailleur-hanger-alignment-tool-2021-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08152812/Park-Tool-DAG-3-derailleur-hanger-alignment-tool-2021-3.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x419/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" alt=\"Park Tool derailleur hanger tool DAG-3\" width=\"900\" height=\"780\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08152812/Park-Tool-DAG-3-derailleur-hanger-alignment-tool-2021-3.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x419/rscb8/ng:webp/ngcb8\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08152812/Park-Tool-DAG-3-derailleur-hanger-alignment-tool-2021-3.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 900w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08152812/Park-Tool-DAG-3-derailleur-hanger-alignment-tool-2021-3-297x257.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/08152812/Park-Tool-DAG-3-derailleur-hanger-alignment-tool-202